data.name: Cheesy Bacon-Wrapped Chicken Thighs
data.quickTastyDescription: Juicy chicken thighs wrapped in crispy bacon and oozing with melted cheese, perfect for a satisfying meal.
detailedCookingInstructions: Season the chicken thighs with garlic powder, paprika, salt, and pepper.
Place a slice of cheddar cheese on each chicken thigh.
Wrap each chicken thigh with two slices of bacon, ensuring the cheese is covered.
Place the wrapped thighs on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.
Bake in the preheated oven for 25-30 minutes, or until the bacon is crispy and the chicken is cooked through.
Let it rest for a few minutes before serving.
data.modifiersForBase: Wrapped in bacon and topped with cheese
